      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STATE OF MADNESS (4) has a strong record this track and trip with six wins and five placings from 18 starts. In the money last time at this track (30.98) in a NG, finishing a 4.5 lengths third. Makes strong appeal on best. PRETTY ESMAY (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at Angle Park in a handy 20.04 beating Life Of Luxury. Should be in this for a long way. RAVEN PETER (8) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 31.28 beating Caruggi. Should feature again. THUNDERING LADY (2) is not to be discarded.",
